deck_description:
i find running 3/2/2/2/2 of Kelbek/Mudora/Agido/Keldo &amp; 1 of both gravekeeper's trap &amp; exchange of the spirit helps brick less

&nbsp;

note: this deck might change a little in future versions

If you have Crimson Resonator, Black Whirlwind, Blackwing - Simoon the Poison Wind, Cards for Black Feathers, and Blackwing - Mistral the Silver Shield, do this. First activate spell Black Whirlwind, then Normal Summon Blackwing - Simoon the Poison Wind without tributing from hand, but you need to banish Blackwing - Mistral the Silver Shield to do that, then activate Black Whirlwind on summon to add Black Wing Monster that can be Special Summoned from hand (I recommend Blackwing - Oroshi the Squall). If you added Blackwing - Oroshi the Squall, Special Summon him, and Synchro using Simoon and Oroshi to Blackwing Tamer - Obsidian Hawk Joe. Then activate Obsidian Hawk Joe's effect to Special Summon Blackwing - Simoon the Poison Wind from GY into Defense Position. That's small combo which I minded of. If you want, you can find more combos for yourselves. Until next time, Goodbye!

